metadata.description: Perform fast, reliable, and secure multi-wallet swaps through our Telegram bot. Our dapp supports multiple chains: Ethereum, Binance, Arbitrum, Polygon, Optimism, and Fantom. Support for additional EVM compatible chains will be added if the need arises. Holding this NFT grants you access to our dTools Black Telegram bot and the utility described.
